        "Assimilation": "Assimilation is a Piagetian concept about fitting new information into existing schemas. It doesn't describe the teaching/support process shown here.",
        "Accommodation": "Accommodation is also Piagetian—modifying schemas when new information doesn't fit. While learning may involve accommodation, the question asks about the teaching process, which is scaffolding.",
